  "text": "The top is ZAP70, a member of the Syk tyrosine kinase family. Recently, Gatalica and Bing [CITATION_1] pointed out that the loss of Syk tyrosine kinase expression characterises a subset of breast carcinomas. This implies a relationship between ZAP70 and breast cancer.",
